Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.61,0:00:07.04,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,I am making this order as Euphemia Li Britannia.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.65,0:00:11.69,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Please kill everyone who calls himself or herself Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:14.82,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Leave no one alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.01,0:01:52.17,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Euphemia betrayed us!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.17,0:01:54.57,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,All forces, charge towards the ceremonial venue!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.57,0:01:56.26,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Break Britannia apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.14,0:02:03.78,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Euphemia... That bitch actually dared to trick us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:09.23,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you Elevens!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.60,0:02:10.15,CG ON,Tohdoh,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.55,0:02:12.59,CG ON,Tohdoh,0000,0000,0000,,So this was your true intention?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.18,0:02:17.53,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Order of the Black Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:19.15,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Defeat Britannia!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.73,0:02:22.43,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,540)}Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:24.01,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Euphie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.29,0:02:29.79,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it. I don't have time to deal with you right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.03,0:02:32.48,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this has turned into a big, big mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.63,0:02:40.67,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,Unforgivable... She actually trampled on everyone's feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.67,0:02:41.55,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,Euphemia!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.84,0:02:45.95,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.88,0:02:49.10,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.59,0:02:53.27,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,How insolent! I am Euphemia Li Britannia!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.28,0:02:58.19,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so this is where you were, you doll princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.46,0:03:01.08,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, you were on that island...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.08,0:03:04.07,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Revenge for everyone shall be dealt here...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.07,0:03:04.62,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,0:03:05.33,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.92,0:03:07.68,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Leave her to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:11.81,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,You are just a Japanese...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.71,0:03:20.19,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do, Zero?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.19,0:03:21.08,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Capture her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.08,0:03:22.59,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That's pointless now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.45,0:03:25.09,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,It's a massacre.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.09,0:03:27.97,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,I must annihilate all the Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.84,0:03:37.34,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Hurry... I must hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:42.30,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Erm... If I remember correctly...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.15,0:03:49.04,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I thought you were one of the Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:51.16,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I thought about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:54.39,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we make the announcement about the Specially Administrated Zone of Nippon together...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.39,0:03:55.88,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Nippon...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:03:56.97,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.65,0:03:59.92,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to do that, if possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.99,0:04:02.13,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Together with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.26,0:04:06.80,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Euphie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.24,0:04:11.05,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.71,0:04:15.73,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Why... Lelouch...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.09,0:04:18.17,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Good bye, Euphie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.88,0:04:21.15,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You were... most likely my first love.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.02,0:04:28.74,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.00,0:04:29.79,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,Why, at a time like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.94,0:04:35.92,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I can't block the Hadron Cannon.{the hard-on Cannon? <_<}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.42,0:04:41.34,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you kill Lelouch...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.17,0:04:45.34,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku!{bled as there's a gap before she says ku - el}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:47.07,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:54.43,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.42,0:05:07.70,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you... Euphie...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.18,0:05:09.68,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Please save Euphie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:14.19,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,You still can't get in touch with Darlton?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.19,0:05:17.54,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, there were reports saying that he had been injured, but after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.95,0:05:20.59,CG ON,Guilford,0000,0000,0000,,Governor-General Cornelia, there's an emergency transmission from the Avalon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.93,0:05:21.90,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,From the Avalon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.90,0:05:22.64,CG ON,Guilford,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.64,0:05:25.76,CG ON,Guilford,0000,0000,0000,,According to them, the Order of the Black Knights has taken over the Specially Administrated Zone around Mount Fuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.11,0:05:27.20,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.20,0:05:29.85,CG ON,Guilford,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that the Order of the Black Knights is already prepared to intercept us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.85,0:05:31.17,CG ON,Guilford,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.29,0:05:33.56,CG ON,Guilford,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Euphemia is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:45.54,CG ON,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,What was that about equality?! The Specially Administrated Zone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.54,0:05:47.84,CG ON,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,You actually dared to trick us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.84,0:05:49.34,CG ON,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,I can no longer forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.34,0:05:51.24,CG ON,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,I definitely can't forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:52.10,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:53.34,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,We can't forgive Britannia!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.34,0:05:54.45,CG ON,???03,0000,0000,0000,,We are Japanese!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.70,0:05:56.20,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this great?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.20,0:05:59.58,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,The movies, tools, and equipment of the ceremonial venue are still around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:04.19,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I'll post them on the Internet after editing, and show them to the entire world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.19,0:06:06.63,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make them realize which side is the side of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.93,0:06:11.30,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, you really have no loyalty to Britannia, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.30,0:06:12.45,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,Loyalty?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.45,0:06:13.32,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.32,0:06:15.83,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,Britannia is a finished product.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:17.68,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point in chasing after something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.94,0:06:21.51,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,You're a more honest person than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.51,0:06:23.26,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,The same goes for you. What do you plan to do from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.26,0:06:24.60,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.60,0:06:26.74,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just after data,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.20,0:06:29.81,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,but I'd feel bad about abandoning you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:32.54,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, Zero is a very interesting man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.61,0:06:35.31,CG ON,Kaguya,0000,0000,0000,,We finally meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.09,0:06:37.23,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,This girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:40.15,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,380)}If I remember correctly, she's Suzaku's relative.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.52,0:06:44.16,CG ON,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,Zero, about what we are going to do from now on, under our guidance....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.16,0:06:45.30,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It's the opposite!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.11,0:06:50.93,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,As the situation stands, ladies and gentlemen from the six major families of Kyoto, I would like you to come under my command.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:51.97,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I will not allow any debate on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.45,0:06:56.60,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You no longer have any other path to take if you want to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:02.90,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,As for Governor-General Cornelia...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.42,0:07:05.68,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,we will contact her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.68,0:07:07.95,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Can she survive the trip back to the government office?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.35,0:07:09.67,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.10,0:07:12.39,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,We will contact His Highness Schneizel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.39,0:07:13.59,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.41,0:07:23.04,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.31,0:07:24.50,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Euphie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:38.71,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Euphie...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:40.60,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I hope that you will tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.05,0:07:43.54,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,why did you give that order?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:45.66,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Order...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.52,0:07:48.53,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.51,0:07:51.08,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.08,0:07:54.91,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku, you are Japanese... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:56.32,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.75,0:07:58.71,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Euphie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.71,0:07:59.41,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:00.04,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.38,0:08:01.60,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.27,0:08:06.73,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,No... I can't... think of that... can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.04,0:08:09.80,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.22,0:08:11.23,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.88,0:08:13.05,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,The ceremony...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.24,0:08:18.22,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,How is... Nippon...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.74,0:08:19.82,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Euphie...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.31,0:08:21.64,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,You don't remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.31,0:08:31.07,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Japanese!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:34.86,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,To all the people who were oppressed by Britannia!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:37.03,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I have always been waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.43,0:08:40.22,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Constantly correcting the mistakes of Britannia from the shadows,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:42.83,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,hoping that they would someday change themselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.84,0:08:47.38,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,However, our hopes were betrayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.38,0:08:49.25,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,By this act of brutality called a "massacre"!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:53.92,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Are all the Japanese happy...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:55.22,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,We can't forgive Euphemia!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:56.12,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Despicable bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.12,0:08:56.90,CG ON,???03,0000,0000,0000,,Witch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.90,0:08:57.32,CG ON,???04,0000,0000,0000,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:08:59.77,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.77,0:09:02.94,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Euphemia truly is the representation of the kindness of Britannia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.94,0:09:06.29,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,She is just a murderer operating behind the façade of building a country!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.80,0:09:08.12,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Did I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.03,0:09:11.02,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,do... well?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.02,0:09:13.10,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Go to hell, Euphemia!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.10,0:09:14.71,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,We won't be fooled any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.71,0:09:15.61,CG ON,???03,0000,0000,0000,,Go die in Britannia!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.00,0:09:18.87,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Euphie... the Specially Administrated Zone is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.80,0:09:24.33,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,a great success!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:28.48,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is very happy... in Nippon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.32,0:09:31.50,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,That's great...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.87,0:09:36.02,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I shall announce here that, from now on, we will regain our independence from Britannia!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.02,0:09:39.56,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,However, that doesn't mean a revival of the previous Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.56,0:09:42.45,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I won't make the foolish mistake of repeating history!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:45.65,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,What we are going to create is a brand new Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.65,0:09:49.38,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,She must have a wide embrace, ready to accept anyone regardless of race, past, and ideals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.38,0:09:51.50,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,A place where the strong won't oppress the weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.50,0:09:52.69,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,A country with dignity!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.16,0:09:54.41,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Her name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.41,0:09:56.50,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,the United States of Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.18,0:10:00.80,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. This is the time to create a new country!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.85,0:10:02.81,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,How strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.05,0:10:06.75,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,I can't... see your face...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.21,0:10:18.20,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,I want to... go to school...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.67,0:10:24.40,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Because... I stopped... halfway...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.40,0:10:26.68,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Euphie, you can still go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.11,0:10:30.71,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, let's go to Ashford Academy together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.71,0:10:34.04,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,It has an interesting student council. Together with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:39.90,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy my share as well... okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.43,0:10:42.57,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,No, Euphie. No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.02,0:10:48.96,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku... meeting you was...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.47,0:11:12.46,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(1000,500)}Zero! Zero! Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.65,0:11:14.06,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,How...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:21.62,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,Area Fukushima: Residential troops are currently moving towards Ibaraki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.62,0:11:25.28,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,Area Tama: We are currently transporting weapons to the unarmed volunteers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.56,0:11:27.43,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,Area Hamamatsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:28.04,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,Are you preparing to attack the Tokyo Settlement?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:29.26,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.94,0:11:32.21,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Now is the best chance to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.01,0:11:36.19,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. The Geass is ineffective against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.19,0:11:37.09,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,You know that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:39.31,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:44.38,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's time to say goodbye to everyone, now that I can't control my Geass.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.39,0:11:48.49,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Nunnally?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.49,0:11:49.88,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.88,0:11:53.17,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Erm... I want to talk to Sister Euphie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.41,0:11:57.90,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, me and her, the three of us can go to the school festival together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:12:03.03,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Milly-san said that, since the school festival was interrupted, she wanted to organize another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.48,0:12:07.10,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I was wondering what we should do then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.10,0:12:09.22,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Erm... sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.22,0:12:11.37,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,You said that we won't be meeting with her again...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.79,0:12:14.11,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,But it's fine no matter what form it takes,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.11,0:12:16.25,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,if we can have direct interactions with her again...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.64,0:12:19.42,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Nunnally, you didn't hear about the news?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:23.08,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,The radio broadcast was terminated halfway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:25.22,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.46,0:12:27.99,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. It's fine then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.99,0:12:31.12,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'll be back tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.12,0:12:32.67,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,We'll discuss it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.80,0:12:34.60,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.74,0:12:40.36,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any changes other than being unable to stop your Geass?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.68,0:12:42.53,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Not really. Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.75,0:12:49.69,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Euphie... wanted to go against... the order I issued with the Geass.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.68,0:12:53.00,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that it might be due to my power weakening...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.49,0:12:54.37,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,But it's most likely...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.41,0:12:58.08,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,to her, the order was something she really, really, couldn't accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.96,0:13:01.67,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It's something... very natural to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:02.40,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.09,0:13:04.50,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.96,0:13:07.16,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:14.48,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,We made a contract, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:18.23,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be the only one... left beside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.62,0:13:22.13,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Things have started to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.13,0:13:25.58,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's been only a few hours since the information was revealed on the Internet,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.58,0:13:27.53,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,riots have started up in various areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.53,0:13:30.26,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,The largest militant organization, the Order of the Black Knights,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.26,0:13:34.71,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,is advancing towards the Tokyo Settlement while absorbing normal civilians into their ranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:36.89,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,The other blocks are currently engaged in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.89,0:13:38.17,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,We can't expect any reinforcements!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.42,0:13:41.99,CG ON,???02s,0000,0000,0000,,Included among the enemy ranks are people who applied to be Honorary Britannians,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.99,0:13:44.02,CG ON,???02s,0000,0000,0000,,and their numbers are in the tens of thousands!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.02,0:13:44.76,CG ON,???03,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Guilford!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.03,0:13:46.18,CG ON,Guilford,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:48.22,CG ON,Guilford,0000,0000,0000,,We can't act without the orders of Her Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.49,0:13:52.21,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,However, since the Govenor-General issued the order to cease combat,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.21,0:13:54.59,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,she has locked herself up in Princess Euphemia's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.59,0:13:58.44,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,In such a situation where General Darlton's whereabouts are still unknown...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:19.09,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Toyama squad. Twenty-three people have joined us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.09,0:14:19.50,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.94,0:14:21.17,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any weapons?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:24.45,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,We have obtained some explosives from Okayama, but we don't have enough vehicles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.45,0:14:25.85,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Can we send some people over to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.85,0:14:28.34,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,The only vehicles left are cargo trucks. Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.76,0:14:31.40,CG ON,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,The group from Yamadashi has joined up as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.40,0:14:34.11,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,The survivors from Samurai Blood have contacted us as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.11,0:14:35.52,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Our numbers have grown quite impressively.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:39.02,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hope that everyone from the student council managed to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.08,0:14:42.08,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.08,0:14:43.96,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,I am happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:48.41,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I had completely forgotten what kindness was,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.41,0:14:49.82,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,Marianne...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.17,0:14:53.51,CG ON,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,Kaname-san, the same goes for you. Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.51,0:14:55.62,CG ON,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember correctly, you are working at Shizuoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.90,0:14:57.91,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, this place is still sort of all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.40,0:15:01.79,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chigusa, there's something important I want to talk to you about when I return...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.68,0:15:03.96,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.48,0:15:07.02,CG ON,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,That's the first time you called me by that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.02,0:15:09.52,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... Sorry... Did you feel awkward?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.52,0:15:10.47,CG ON,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:12.02,CG ON,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait for you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.71,0:15:16.81,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Here she is, that Britannian bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:18.21,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,You were looking outside earlier, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.21,0:15:20.27,CG ON,???03,0000,0000,0000,,You are a spy! You are a spy, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.77,0:15:24.78,CG ON,Announcement,0000,0000,0000,,As rebel troops draw closer, public order in the ghetto is deteriorating.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.78,0:15:29.46,CG ON,Announcement,0000,0000,0000,,Dear citizens, please do not leave your houses until given notice by the administration.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.46,0:15:31.97,CG ON,Announcement,0000,0000,0000,,Currently at the Settlement...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.34,0:15:32.70,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Will this place turn into a battlefield as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:34.67,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,H-How can that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.67,0:15:37.44,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Govenor-General Cornelia's regular army is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.44,0:15:38.26,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,It won't. It won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.26,0:15:39.85,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.85,0:15:42.55,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say such things. It's scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.99,0:15:45.89,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Nunnally, Lelouch hasn't return home yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.89,0:15:47.26,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,L-Lelouch?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.26,0:15:48.44,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.44,0:15:50.00,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ah... It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.64,0:15:52.99,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Just call him Lulu already.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.99,0:15:54.14,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, patch things up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.42,0:15:55.27,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,"Lulu"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.20,0:15:58.22,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Was that what I called him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.22,0:16:00.57,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,You are still saying such things...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.88,0:16:03.02,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Lulu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:07.01,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Nina, go back to the floor of the school building.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.01,0:16:08.92,CG ON,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,The rebel troops are approaching Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.49,0:16:11.65,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,I know. Zero will come, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.84,0:16:16.51,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait, Princess Euphemia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.51,0:16:19.56,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,416)}I'll definitely avenge you. {by masturbating against a KnightMare this time?}{lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.46,0:16:24.19,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Euphie... I don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.19,0:16:26.32,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you do such a thing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.32,0:16:27.94,CG ON,V.V.,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.78,0:16:30.74,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,A child?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.26,0:16:32.80,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you on the Avalon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.20,0:16:35.65,CG ON,V.V,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, Kururugi Suzaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:38.14,CG ON,V.V.,0000,0000,0000,,I am V.V..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.41,0:16:40.18,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,V.V.?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.55,0:16:50.26,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,The Atsugi line has been breached!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.26,0:16:51.72,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,What about reinforcements from the main country?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.72,0:16:53.10,CG ON,???03,0000,0000,0000,,It's already too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.10,0:16:55.39,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Then we should abandon this area...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.39,0:16:56.46,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Don't panic!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.87,0:16:59.95,CG ON,Guilford,0000,0000,0000,,P-Princess Cornelia!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.27,0:17:02.79,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,I already have the Graston Knights on standby.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:05.53,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Deploy all troops to the other edge of the Tokyo Settlement.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.53,0:17:09.00,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we eliminate the Order of the Black Knights and Zero, the rebellion will be suppressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.25,0:17:12.04,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It's our victory once we bring down Cornelia!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.04,0:17:15.36,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,All troops, position yourself based on the combat deployment map!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.11,0:17:18.83,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Diethard, leave the frontlines to Tohdoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.83,0:17:20.60,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave this place to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.00,0:17:21.93,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.63,0:17:25.03,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Sumeragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.03,0:17:26.79,CG ON,Kaguya,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness! I made it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.36,0:17:31.26,CG ON,Kaguya,0000,0000,0000,,How mean! You intended to leave me aside and head off into battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.26,0:17:35.17,CG ON,Kaguya,0000,0000,0000,,I have been a fan of yours ever since your début.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.17,0:17:37.91,CG ON,Kaguya,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking that I'd finally get a chance to have a good talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:40.45,CG ON,Kaguya,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you are surprisingly tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.45,0:17:43.20,CG ON,Kaguya,0000,0000,0000,,But it's fine, I'll catch up with you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.41,0:17:48.31,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kaguya-sama, isn't everyone from the six major families staying at Fuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.31,0:17:49.73,CG ON,Kaguya,0000,0000,0000,,I chased after you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.73,0:17:51.84,CG ON,Kaguya,0000,0000,0000,,In order to see how my husband fights!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.05,0:17:53.05,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:54.05,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.46,0:17:58.55,CG ON,Kaguya,0000,0000,0000,,You need a wife after you win this battle, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.55,0:18:03.77,CG ON,Kaguya,0000,0000,0000,,Since you can't reveal your identity, I think that you might need someone to compensate for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:06.93,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think we can win this battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.28,0:18:10.10,CG ON,Kaguya,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, because I'm the goddess of victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.54,0:18:12.16,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That sure is dependable.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.16,0:18:16.59,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,But, unfortunately, I've already bound a contract with the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.59,0:18:17.03,CG ON,Kaguya,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.43,0:18:21.32,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,As things are now, I don't think I can get along with Gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.03,0:18:27.34,CG ON,Bartley,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.34,0:18:29.52,CG ON,Bartley,0000,0000,0000,,We have to send the experimental specimen to the main country...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.52,0:18:30.67,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,The pressure is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.67,0:18:32.63,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,The internal pressure is building up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.36,0:18:40.51,CG ON,Bartley,0000,0000,0000,,At such a time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.05,0:18:48.99,CG ON,Orange,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:53.81,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, Britannia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.81,0:18:55.17,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I am Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.98,0:18:58.72,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,A rebel against those with power!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.39,0:19:01.10,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait until 0:00 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.10,0:19:02.95,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Surrender and submit to my army.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.34,0:19:05.31,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,This is my ultimatum.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.31,0:19:06.69,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait until 0:00 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.69,0:19:08.47,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Surrender and submit to my army.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.87,0:19:16.39,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,General Darlton, it's indeed impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.39,0:19:17.42,CG ON,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.42,0:19:19.82,CG ON,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,I must go to where the princess... the princess is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.39,0:19:22.81,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pointless threat, Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.81,0:19:25.39,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,The Tokyo Settlement can be considered a fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.72,0:19:29.98,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,You can still head back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.70,0:19:33.12,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,You won't involve just Area 11 if this goes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.76,0:19:38.03,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,Your life, along with the entire world, will be engulfed by constant battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.32,0:19:39.65,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.13,0:19:41.39,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:46.37,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Euphie?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.37,0:19:48.29,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Impossible, how could she know my number?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.71,0:19:51.21,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, there's someone that knows it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.20,0:19:58.00,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.58,0:19:59.71,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.27,0:20:01.59,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you calling at such an hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.93,0:20:04.26,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch, are you at school right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.51,0:20:07.02,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,No, but I'll be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.47,0:20:08.18,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.54,0:20:11.60,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I called because there's something I want to tell everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.07,0:20:14.03,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,At such a time? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.03,0:20:17.16,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I... I hope that you won't look at the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.16,0:20:18.02,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.74,0:20:19.74,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.58,0:20:24.28,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,is there someone you hate so much that you want to kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:27.20,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.95,0:20:31.20,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I always felt that I shouldn't think that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.20,0:20:35.34,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,That if I don't follow the rules during a fight, I'll just be a murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.72,0:20:40.25,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,However, hatred consumes me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.78,0:20:43.67,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I am going into battle to kill someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.23,0:20:47.89,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Above the sky of Tokyo, where everyone lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.89,0:20:48.58,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,commit murder...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.14,0:20:49.96,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,That is why...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.96,0:20:51.31,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine to feel hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.63,0:20:53.03,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It's for Euphie's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.03,0:20:55.59,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I've made up my mind as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.04,0:20:57.72,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I don't intend to head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.37,0:20:59.69,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Is it for Nunnally's sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.69,0:21:00.27,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.37,0:21:02.69,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for me to hang up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.99,0:21:04.86,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.86,0:21:06.35,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.35,0:21:08.80,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,We are friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.80,0:21:10.63,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,We've always been, ever since seven years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.63,0:21:12.51,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.51,0:21:14.29,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Bye then. See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.96,0:21:21.71,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.72,0:21:34.78,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku, my hands have long since been stained.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.78,0:21:37.64,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, it's fine if you come forth to challenge me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.64,0:21:39.36,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I'll entertain you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:41.98,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It's because we are friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.65,0:21:57.83,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Perhaps I have desired this ever since that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.83,0:22:00.41,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The destruction and reconstruction of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.41,0:22:04.14,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right. Destruction is needed before reconstruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.14,0:22:07.07,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If my feelings become a hindrance in the process,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.07,0:22:09.24,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it's best that I eliminate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.24,0:22:13.43,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right, I have no choice but to proceed forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.81,0:22:14.77,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That is why...
